<font color="#FF0000">GOD BLESS THE NURSES</font><br>
<tt>Mon Dec 23 14:31:40 US/Eastern 1996
</tt><p>
God Bless the nurses of Vietnam.  What they must have seen in those field hospitals, when young men were sent in wounded in all kinds of conditions.  There service must have been every bit as trying and painful as being out in the field fighting the NVA/VC.  Their stories need to be told and added to the fabric of the oral history of Vietnam.  Their service should always be remembered.
